# coeai

Python client for interacting with the hosted LLM model via HTTP.

## Installation

```bash
pip install .
Usage
python
Copy
Edit
from coeai import LLMinfer

llm = LLMinfer(api_url="http://your-server:8000/generate", api_key="your-api-key")

# Text-to-text inference
result = llm.infer(mode="text-to-text", prompt_text="Who are you?")
print(result)

# Image + text inference
result = llm.infer(mode="image-text-to-text", prompt_text="Describe this image", image_path="my_image.jpg")
print(result)
yaml
